    the entries when appropriate to suit your identity as a cloistered scholar.","Your
    bond is almost certainly associated either with the place where you grew up or
    with the knowledge you hope to acquire through adventuring. Your ideal is no
    doubt related to how you view the quest for knowledge and truth - perhaps as
    a worthy goal in itself, or maybe as a means to a desirable end."]}],"hasFluff":true}'
